p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Steven Zahm";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3667:"<p>The CSV Import Extension has received a significant update. The most notable improvements are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Much improved documentation on the plugin’s admin pages.</li>\n<li>More efficient importing requiring fewer database queries which means importing happens a little quicker. Further improvements to import efficiencies will be gained when Connections 0.8 is released.</li>\n<li>Imports now happen in small batches rather than all at once for more reliable imports when importing large CSV files. During testing a CSV file with more than 10,000 records on a shared webhost with very limited server resources. In all tests it imported reliably.</li>\n<li>Now fully supports importing data to all core fields within Connections, except photos and images.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third last">		<!--dynamic-cached-content-->\n		<form id="edd_purchase_2721" class="edd_download_purchase_form" method="post">\n\n			\n			<div class="edd_purchase_submit_wrapper">\n\n				<span class="edd_button_shell edd_color_royalgreen"><a href="#" class="edd-add-to-cart " data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2721" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single ><span class="edd-add-to-cart-label">&#036;14.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart</span> <span class="edd-loading"><i class="edd-icon-spinner edd-icon-spin"></i></span></a><input type="submit" class="edd-add-to-cart edd-no-js " name="edd_purchase_download" value="&#036;14.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart" data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2721" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single /><a href="https://connections-pro.com/shopping-cart/" class="edd_go_to_checkout button" style="display:none;">Checkout</a></span><!--end .edd_button_shell-->\n									<span class="edd-cart-ajax-alert">\n						<div><span class="edd-cart-added-alert" style="display: none;">\n							<i class="edd-icon-ok"></i> Item added to cart.						</span></div>\n					</span>\n				\n			</div><!--end .edd_purchase_submit_wrapper-->\n\n			\n			<input type="hidden" name="download_id" value="2721">\n							<input type="hidden" name="edd_action" class="edd_action_input" value="add_to_cart">\n			\n			\n		</form><!--end #edd_purchase_2721-->\n		<!--/dynamic-cached-content-->\n	</div><div class="clearboth"></div>\n<p><strong>Changelog:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>= 1.0.3 11/17/2013 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>BUG:</strong> Fix a possible fatal error when importing a CSV with no categories.</li>\n<li><strong>OTHER:</strong> Comment out a couple unused JavaScript variables.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 1.0.2 11/17/2013 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>TWEAK:</strong> Increase import segment from 100 to 500.</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK:</strong> Use jqXHR Object method .always() to process data import segment response data and fire off the recursive function.</li>\n<li><strong>BUG:</strong> Fix an instance where the &#8220;Uncategorized&#8221; category was being assigned to entries in which it should have not.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 1.0.1 11/16/2013 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>TWEAK:</strong> Updated styles to include support for pre Connections 0.8.</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK:</strong> Updated styles to include support for pre WP 3.8.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 1.0 11/16/2013 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete rewrite.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2013/11/18/extension-update-csv-import-1-0-3/">Extension Update: CSV Import 1.0.3</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n<img src="//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro-modules/~4/NpR53G00x-M" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:77:"http://connections-pro.com/2013/11/18/extension-update-csv-import-1-0-3/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"http://connections-pro.com/2013/11/18/extension-update-csv-import-1-0-3/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:54:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"Pro Module Update: Link 1.0.2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:70:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/connections-pro-modules/~3/VwaEP0KjfCg/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/19/pro-module-update-link-1-0-2/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 19 Mar 2013 22:52:53 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Pro Mod