:"<p>Market has received a significant update to take full advantage of all the newer features built into Connections.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/27/template-update-market-3-0/">Template Update: Market 3.0</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Steven Zahm";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2986:"<p>Market has received a significant update to take full advantage of all the newer features built into Connections.</p>\n<div class="note"><h4 class="note_title">Important</h4><div class="note_content">Market 3.0 takes advantage of the new and improved template system introduced in version 0.7.6 of Connections. Please read the following installation instructions.</p>\n<p>If you are upgrading from an older version of Market you must go to the Connections : Templates admin page and delete the older version before installing the new version.</p>\n<p>To install the new version, please install it as you would any plugin, please do not use the template installer found on the Connections : Templates admin page. The template installer will only remain in place until all templates have been updated to use the new templating system. After which it will be removed completely.</p>\n<p>After you install Market , as a plugin, activate it as a plugin.</p>\n<p>Finally, after Market has been activated, it will show up on the Connections : Templates admin page and be available for use.</div></div>\n<div class="clearboth"></div>\n<div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third last">		<!--dynamic-cached-content-->\n	