cn-list" data-connections-version="8.1.5-0.1.9"><div class="cn-template cn-slim" id="cn-slim" data-template-version="3.0">\n<div class="cn-list-head cn-clear" id="cn-list-head">\n\n</div>\n\n<div class="connections-list cn-list-body cn-clear" id="cn-list-body">\n<div class="cn-list-section-head" id="cn-char-D"></div><div class="cn-list-row-alternate vcard individual uncategorized" id="jane-doe-2" data-entry-type="individual" data-entry-id="195" data-entry-slug="jane-doe-2">\n<div id="entry-id-1955486aae4a12a2" class="cn-entry">\n\n	<h3 class="cn-accordion-item" data-div-id="cn-detail-1955486aae4a12a2" style="border-bottom: #660066 1px solid; color:#660066;"><span class="cn-sprite" style="background-color: #660066;"></span>\n<span class="fn n"> <span class="given-name">Jane</span> <span class="family-name">Doe</span> </span>\n</h3><div class="cn-detail cn-clear cn-hide" id="cn-detail-1955486aae4a12a2"><div class="cn-left">\n<span class="cn-image-style" style="display: inline-block;"><span class="cn-image-photo cn-image-none" style="width: 100px; height: 120px; display: inline-block;"><span>No Photo Available</span></span></span>\n</div><div class="cn-right">\n<span class="address-block">\n<span class="adr"><span class="address-name">Home</span> <span class="street-address">123 Sample Street</span> <span class="locality">Lancaster</span> <span class="region">PA</span> <span class="postal-code">12345</span> <span class="type" style="display: none;">home</span></span>\n</span>\n\n<span class="phone-number-block">\n<span class="tel"><span class="phone-name">Cell Phone</span><span class="cn-separator">:</span> <span class="value">717-555-1235</span><span class="type" style="display: none;">cell</span></span>\n</span>\n\n<span class="date-block">\n<span class="vevent"><span class="date-name">Anniversary</span><span class="cn-separator">:</span> <abbr class="dtstart" title="20150219">February 19, 2015</abbr><span class="summary" style="display:none">Anniversary - </span><span class="uid" style="display:none">20150219000000</span></span> <span class="vevent"><span class="date-name">Birthday</span><span class="cn-separator">:</span> <abbr class="dtstart" title="20151002">October 2, 2015</abbr><span class="summary" style="display:none">Birthday - </span><span class="uid" style="display:none">20151002000000</span></span>\n</span>\n\n<span class="link-block">\n<span class="link personal"><span class="link-name">Website</span><span class="cn-separator">:</span> <a class="url" href="http://connections-pro.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://connections-pro.com</a></span>\n</span>\n</div></div></div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class="cn-clear" id="cn-list-foot">\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Pretty nifty, right? You can use any valid CSS color to match the color scheme of your theme.</p>\n<p>Here are a couple sample shortcodes to show you how:</p>\n\n<div class="wp_syntax"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre class="css" style="font-family:monospace;"><span style="color: #808080; font-style: italic;">/*\n * Change the color to red:\n */</span>\n<span style="color: #00AA00;">&#91;</span>connections template<span style="color: #00AA00;">=</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">''slim''</span> <span style="color: #000000; font-weight: bold;">color</span><span style="color: #00AA00;">=</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">''red''</span><span style="color: #00AA00;">&#93;</span>\n&nbsp;\n<span style="color: #808080; font-style: italic;">/*\n * Change the color to plum:\n */</span>\n<span style="color: #00AA00;">&#91;</span>connections template<span style="color: #00AA00;">=</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">''slim''</span> <span style="color: #000000; font-weight: bold;">color</span><span style="color: #00AA00;">=</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">''#660066''</span><span style="color: #00AA00;">&#93;</span></pre></td></tr></table></div>\n\n<div class="note"><h4 class="note_title">Important</h4><div class="note_content">Slim 2.0 takes advantage of the new and improved template system introduced in version 0.7.6 of Connections. Please read the following installation instructions.</p>\n<p>If you are upgrading from an older version of Slim you must go to the Connections : Templates admin page and delete the older version before installing the new version.</p>\n<p>To install the new version, please install it as you would any plugin, please do not use the template installer found on the Connections : Templates admin page. The template installer will only remain in place until all templates have been updated to use the new templating system. After which it will be removed completely.</p>\n<p>After you install Slim, as a plugin, activate it as a plugin.</p>\n<p>Finally, after Slim has been activated, it will show up on the Connections : Templates admin page and be available for use.</div></div>\n<div class="clearboth"></div>\n<div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third last">		<!--dynamic-cached-content-->\n		<form id="edd_purchase_2715" class="edd_download_purchase_form" method="post">\n\n			\n			<div class="edd_purchase_submit_wrapper">\n\n				<span class="edd_button_shell edd_color_royalgreen"><a href="#" class="edd-add-to-cart " data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2715" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single ><span class="edd-add-to-cart-label">&#036;9.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart</span> <span class="edd-loading"><i class="edd-icon-spinner edd-icon-spin"></i></span></a><input type="submit" class="edd-add-to-cart edd-no-js " name="edd_purchase_download" value="&#036;9.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart" data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2715" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single /><a href="https://connections-pro.com/shopping-cart/" class="edd_go_to_checkout button" style="display:none;">Checkout</a></span><!--end .edd_button_shell-->\n									<span class="edd-cart-ajax-alert">\n						<div><span class="edd-cart-added-alert" style="display: none;">\n							<i class="edd-icon-ok"></i> Item added to cart.						</span></div>\n					</span>\n				\n			</div><!--end .edd_purchase_submit_wrapper-->\n\n			\n			<input type="hidden" name="download_id" value="2715">\n							<input type="hidden" name="edd_action" class="edd_action_input" value="add_to_cart">\n			\n			\n		</form><!--end #edd_purchase_2715-->\n		<!--/dynamic-cached-content-->\n	</div><div class="clearboth"></div>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/16/template-update-slim-2-0/">Template Update: Slim 2.0</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n<img src="//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-templates/~4/rlZ_t7cApE8" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/16/template-update-slim-2-0/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/16/template-update-slim-2-0/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:54:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:30:"Template Update: Tile Plus 2.1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0: