.7.2.6 to be installed. = 2.0.2 4/22/2012 = BUG: When searching for terms that returned no results; the search showed all entries. Now the &#8216;No Results&#8217; message will be returned. = 2.0.1 2/15/2012 = BUG: Added missing option arrays to support some shortcode ...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2012/04/22/template-update-tile-plus-2-0-2/">Template Update: Tile Plus 2.0.2</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Steven Zahm";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:841:"<p>Tile Plus has received a few bug fixes. <strong>Very imported</strong>: this fix requires that Connections 0.7.2.6 to be installed.</p>\n<h4>= 2.0.2 4/22/2012 =</h4>\n<p><strong>BUG:</strong> When searching for terms that returned no results; the search showed all entries. Now the &#8216;No Results&#8217; message will be returned.</p>\n<h4>= 2.0.1 2/15/2012 =</h4>\n<p><strong>BUG:</strong> Added missing option arrays to support some shortcode options for the address, phone and email blocks.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2012/04/22/template-update-tile-plus-2-0-2/">Template Update: Tile Plus 2.0.2</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com">Connections</a>.</p>\n<img src="//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-templates/~4/yuq3TQKRsWg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://connections-pro.com/2012/04/22/template-up